==其他資料==
在1990年代起，007系列電影逐漸受到許多世界知名企業的注目，開始與片商合作在影片中製造自家產品的曝光機會，而使得該系列電影變成[[置入性行銷|置入性行銷]]的著名範例。曾經投資贊助過影片拍攝的主要廠商包括[[Aston_Martin|Aston Martin]]、[[BMW|BMW]]、[[勞斯萊斯|勞斯萊斯]]、[[福特汽車|福特]]、[[Audi|Audi]]等汽車集團，電腦/通訊大廠[[新力易利信|-{zh-hans:索尼爱立信;zh-hk:新力愛力信;zh-tw:新力易利信;}-]]（Sony Ericsson，[[索尼|索尼]]与[[爱立信|爱立信]]合资品牌），另外如[[卡尔·瓦尔特运动枪有限公司|瓦尔特]]（Walther，[[德國|德國]]槍械製造商）與[[歐米茄|歐米茄]]（OMEGA，[[瑞士|瑞士]]鐘錶廠，[[斯沃琪集團|斯沃琪集團]]旗下）在該系列電影中都有非常高的曝光度。

不少其他國家的作品都把故事的特務角色以他作參考，不論是現代還是古裝。[[周星馳|周星馳]]的《[[國產凌凌漆|國產凌凌漆]]》（''From China With Love''或''From Beijing With Love''，英文戲名仿原版007电影''From Russia With Love''）和《[[大內密探零零發|大內密探零零發]]》的主角都或多或少影射詹姆士·龐德。

根據波蘭國家紀念研究所檔案，真人版占士邦（James Albert Bond, {{bd|1928年||2005年||catIdx=F}}）於1964年2月18日入該國受聘為英國大使館武官的檔案保管員。他被指於波蘭期間試圖「滲透」當地軍事設施。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.singtao.ca/4508305/2020-09-24/news-%E5%8D%A0%E5%A3%AB%E9%82%A6%E7%9C%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E8%AD%891960%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3James+Bond%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD/?variant=zh-hk |title=占士邦真有其人？國家檔案證1960年代James Bond出沒波蘭 |access-date=2021-08-17 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027025631/https://www.singtao.ca/4508305/2020-09-24/news-%E5%8D%A0%E5%A3%AB%E9%82%A6%E7%9C%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E8%AD%891960%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3James+Bond%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=007’s file found in the IPN’s Archive|url=http://ipn.gov.pl/en/news/4634,007s-file-found-in-the-IPNs-Archive.html|accessdate=2020-10-23|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125024322/https://ipn.gov.pl/en/news/4634,007s-file-found-in-the-IPNs-Archive.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他亦有個叫占士邦的兒子，出生於1955年。<ref>東周刊 EASTWEEK 893期·Book A·波蘭檔案揭秘　特務占士邦真有其人</ref><ref>《星島日報》(STAR MAGAZINE)溫哥華版VOL.977 (2020.10.11)·波蘭檔案揭秘　特務占士邦真有其人</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/09/23/james-bond-man-interested-women-infiltrating-bases-really-did/ |title=James Bond, a man interested in 'women' and 'infiltrating bases', really did spy for Britain in the 1960s |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002024021/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/09/23/james-bond-man-interested-women-infiltrating-bases-really-did/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[亞士頓·馬田|亞士頓·馬田]]的[[窩域郡|窩域郡]]工廠内有部叫「占士邦打」（James Bonder）的擠膠水機，專門黏鋁車殻及擋風玻璃。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://astonmartins.com/db9-production-at-am-gaydon-20034/ |title=DB9 Production at Gaydon |access-date=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108180727/https://astonmartins.com/db9-production-at-am-gaydon-20034/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.business-live.co.uk/manufacturing/aston-martin-james-bond-two-8344725 |title=Aston Martin and James Bond: Two brands inextricably linked |access-date=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029201409/https://www.business-live.co.uk/manufacturing/aston-martin-james-bond-two-8344725 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/2016/10/05/aston-martin-ceo-forget-tesla-well-lead-with-ultra-luxury-electric-vehicles.html |title=Aston Martin CEO: Forget Tesla, we’ll lead with ultra-luxury electric vehicles |access-date=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113912/https://www.cnbc.com/2016/10/05/aston-martin-ceo-forget-tesla-well-lead-with-ultra-luxury-electric-vehicles.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

